dc_description_s: This data represents zoning for Jefferson County, Wisconsin in 2021 and includes the layers 'Jefferson_General_2021' and 'Jefferson_Shoreland_2018' and the table 'JEFFERSON_ZONING_CODES_2021.' While the general zoning data is current to 2021, the shoreland zoning data is dated 2018. Both layers were submitted as part of the '2021 WLIP Call for Data' by the Wisconsin Department of Administration and are included here in one geodatabase for the convenience of the user. [General: This file contains the polygons for all parcels in Jefferson County and the data related to the zoning designation for all tax parcels.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
